Subject: Re: [T2] firewall clearance

What I do is wrap a piece of masking tape around the drill bit until it
becomes fairly thick.
So if you only wanted to go 1" deep, wrap the tape 1" higher and when you
hit the tape, you won't go any further.
Of course, this only works if you know how deep you have to go.
--Nick


